'''黄腹丽唐纳雀'''（''Piranga ludoviciana''）是一种中型的[[美洲|美洲]][[鳴禽|鳴禽]]。黄腹丽唐纳雀曾經被歸類為[[裸鼻雀科|裸鼻雀科]]，目前被歸類為[[主紅雀科|主紅雀科]]。該物種為[[單型|单型]]，目前沒發現任何[[亞種|亞種]]<ref name=ioc>{{cite web | editor1-last=Gill | editor1-first=Frank | editor1-link=Frank Gill (ornithologist) | editor2-last=Donsker | editor2-first=David | editor3-last=Rasmussen | editor3-first=Pamela | editor3-link=Pamela Rasmussen | year=2020 | title=Cardinals, grosbeaks and (tanager) allies | work=IOC World Bird List Version 10.2 | url=https://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/cardinals/ | publisher=International Ornithologists' Union | access-date=1 October 2020 | archive-date=2019-03-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190320213249/https://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/cardinals/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1811年，美国鸟类学家{{link-en|亚历山大·威尔逊|Alexander Wilson (ornithologist)}}根據[[刘易斯与克拉克远征|刘易斯与克拉克远征]]采集到的樣本正式对黄腹丽唐纳雀進行命名<ref>{{Cite book|last=Wilson|first=Alexander|authorlink=Alexander Wilson (ornithologist)|year=1811|title=American Ornithology; or, the Natural History of the Birds of the United States: Illustrated with Plates Engraved and Colored from Original drawings taken from Nature|volume=Volume 3|location=Philadelphia|publisher=Bradford and Inskeep|page=27-28, Plate 20 fig. 1|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/46337745|access-date=2021-02-16|archive-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213002026/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/46337745|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

